Vuyo Dabula (amụrụ na 11 Septemba 1976) bụ onye South Africa na-eme ihe nlereanya, onye na-eme ihe nkiri na onye na-ewu ahụ. A maara ya nke ọma maka ọrụ ya dị ka Shandu Magwaza na ihe nkiri mpụ Netflix, Queen Sono
Ọ gụrụ akwụkwọ na P.H Moeketsi Agricultural High ebe ọ gụrụ akwụkwọ n'afọ 1995, Wits Technikon sochiri ya, ebe ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ mgbe otu afọ gachara n'afọ 1996
O kwuru na ihe ọ gụrụ n'ụlọ akwụkwọ abụghị ihe ọ nwere mmasị ịrụ ọrụ ya maka ọdịnihu; kama ọ malitere ime ihe nkiri
Maka ikwado onwe ya maka ime ihe nkiri, ọ gụrụ akwụkwọ na AFDA Cape Town.
A maara ya nke ọma maka ọrụ ya nke Kumkani Phakade na ncha South Africa, Generations Vuyo pụtakwara na Avengers: Age of Ultron (2015)

Ọ rụkwara ọrụ dị mkpa na ihe nkiri 2017 Five Fingers for Marseilles Vuyo na-eme ihe nkiri ugbu a dị ka Shandu, onye nledo ghọrọ onye nnupụisi yana mmasị ịhụnanya na agwa Pearl Thusi na usoro mbụ nke Netflix, Queen Sono. N'ọnwa Eprel 2020, Netflix megharịrị usoro ahụ maka oge nke abụọ. Otú ọ dị, na Nọvemba 26, 2020, a kọrọ na Netflix akagbuola usoro ahụ n'ihi ihe ịma aka mmepụta nke ọrịa COVID-19 kpatara.
